Question.Subject: Wireless internet signal?
Question.Content: Usually, the internet signal from my computer allows my laptop to get the internet. Its not doing that today. Other than waiting or contacting someone over the phone, how do I resolve this? I have a few people living here so Im not satisfied with just one computer.. To the first answer, I have no idea what youre talking about. Please be more visual and descriptive.
Question.ChosenAnswer: find the router, look at the back of it and you'll see a little reset button, most likely you'll have to use a pen or toothpick to push it. push the reset button and hold it in for about 10-20 seconds until the router lights change color, then give it about 2-3 minutes and try connecting through your laptop then.
